Summary of Compliance
•	Data Collection: No data is collected, stored, or shared.
•	Permissions: Limited to host permissions (https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/*) for applying visual highlights.
•	Local Processing: All functionalities operate entirely within your browser.
________________________________________
FAQs About Privacy
Q1: Does the extension track my activity on LinkedIn?
No, the extension does not monitor or log your activity. It only highlights job statuses and user-defined keywords on LinkedIn job pages.
Q2: Are any external servers contacted?
No. The extension does not make network requests or communicate with external servers.
Q3: How secure is this extension?
The extension is entirely client-side, meaning all processing happens within your browser without any external dependencies.

